.TH "vmw_surface_dma_size" 9 "vmw_surface_dma_size" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vmw_surface_dma_size \- Compute fifo size for a dma command.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "uint32_t" vmw_surface_dma_size
.BI "(const struct vmw_surface *srf "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "srf" 12
Pointer to a struct vmw_surface
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Computes the required size for a surface dma command for backup or
restoration of the surface represented by \fIsrf\fP.
